translation.Name: Easter Note - Alpha #1
translation.Interactability_Text_Line_2: Yesterday we had a research vessel go out to gather some Acropora Cervicornis from the local coral reefs, but the ship never returned. It’s last record position was towards the South West of the island. We should probably send out a rescue party to find them. Really hope that freak thunderstorm last night didn’t take out their ship…
